data.description: Discover the perfect blend of style, comfort, and entertainment in this exceptional 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom home. Nestled in a tranquil neighborhood, this property boasts a range of modern features that make it a true standout. Dive into your own private oasis! Whether you're enjoying a refreshing swim or unwinding in the inviting hot tub, this backyard retreat is your personal haven for relaxation and enjoyment. Rest easy knowing that this home has recently received upgrades to its HVAC system and roof, ensuring not only your comfort but also long-term peace of mind. Custom cabinets provide ample storage and add a touch of elegance to the space, making meal preparation a breeze. Experience the spaciousness and flow of an open concept design that seamlessly connects the kitchen, dining, and living areas. This layout encourages togetherness while still providing distinct spaces for relaxation and entertainment. A dedicated game room offers endless possibilities for fun and relaxation. Elegant tile floors span throughout the entire home, offering both style and practicality.
